&lt;p&gt;I have some code and when it executes, it throws an exception saying:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;The model item passed into the dictionary is of type Bar but this dictionary requires a model item of type Foo&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

